So we need to show `k - m - n Ōēż w`.
But we know `k Ōēż xs.length = m + n + w`.
So `k Ōēż m + n + w`.
Subtracting `m + n` from both sides: `k - (m + n) Ōēż w`.
Which is exactly `k - m - n Ōēż w`.

